Yesterday, the UN proposed in Cancún a plan for the restoration of home lighting, the lighting of shops and industrial space in 100 countries, with a view to achieving a reduction in the greenhouse effect (GES), which corresponds to almost one third of the additional restrictions to be achieved for the stability of the planet's climate from now until 2020.
